data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! MOTIVATED SELLER  Nestled in the heart of Trinidad, in NE Washington D.C., this charming rowhouse duplex is ideal for owner-occupants looking for rental income, multigenerational families, or savvy investors.  The first unit spans two levels, featuring a cozy 1-bedroom with updated kitchen and bathroom on the first level and a lower-level recreation room & laundry room for relaxation, entertainment, and convenience.  The second unit offers a 1-bedroom with and updated kitchen, and  vintage-style bathroom.   Each unit has an in-unit washer and dryer, updated paint & windows, and shared access to a fenced backyard with a driveway.   Situated just steps from Gallaudet University, KIPP DC College Preparatory, the vibrant Union Market, Ivy City commercial district, and the tranquil National Arboretum. The area caters to commuters and cyclists alike, with easy access to the Red Line and bike lanes. Currently vacant, this property is ready for immediate occupancy and comes with a transferable Certificate of Occupancy.
